    dc:description "Fig. 1. Siculobata (Paraleius) americana sp. n., adult: A = dorsal view (legs not shown); B = ventral view (gnathosoma and legs not shown); C = lateral view (gnathosoma and legs not shown). Scale bar 50 Μm" ;
